text: Bobby Madden (12 December 1928 - 21 January 2008) was an Australian cricketer. He played seven first-class matches for New South Wales between 1949/50 and 1959/60. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1928 births Category:2008 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
